column3: This should never have been merged in the first place, I'm happy this concerns an unused function but we should mark consensus-critical files at some point to prevent wallet and RPC PRs from affecting consensus-critical code accidentally.\n\nutACK fa5c511a832632b964617776eb6c3535bb2bd893

Post-merge utACK. Terribly sorry about that. I must've screwed up something between branches.\n\nI went through the merged code to make sure no other accidental code was included as well, and couldn't find any, FWIW.
